    "summary": {
      "title": "Summary",
      "columns": 1,
      "hidden": false,
      "content": "<p><strong>Python</strong> Backend with <strong>+15</strong> years building production systems: APIs (<strong>FastAPI, Django</strong>), complex integrations (<strong>REST, XMLRPC, SOA</strong>), automation and legacy system migration. Specialist in ERP implementations with <strong>Odoo</strong>, electronic invoicing, and <strong>ETL</strong> processes on <strong>PostgreSQL</strong>. I manage my own infrastructure (<strong>Proxmox, Docker, CI/CD</strong>) where I develop, test and deploy end-to-end solutions. Experience across multiple sectors: finance, retail, manufacturing, telecommunications and services. I complement my backend profile with hands-on <strong>AI Engineering</strong> experience: designing <strong>RAG</strong> pipelines, autonomous agents with <strong>LLMs</strong>, and open-source model evaluation, applying AI as a tool to solve real business problems.</p>"
    },
