            "phone": "",
            "description": "You are a natural tech enthusiast. Your tireless drive to learn, discover and apply technology makes you a professional with an astonishing breadth of action. Great qualities for organization, analysis and problem solving, teamwork and an admirable spirit of self-improvement.\n\nAs they would say in sports jargon: \"Give me Rafnix, always!\"\n\nGreat professional and even better person"
