            "phone": "",
            "description": "Great friend and excellent mentor. I have learned a lot working with Rafnix, he has great knowledge in different web technologies, can program in PHP, Javascript, Python and knows a lot about Odoo ERP. He is a technology enthusiast who inspires his work group. He has the ability to analyze the most challenging problems and find the best solution using all his knowledge, and he has the ability to express his ideas clearly and precisely."
